swBpduProtectionMIB.name: swBpduProtectionMIB

swBpduProtectionPortEntry.description: The table specifies the BPDU Protection function specified by port.

swBpduProtectionPortIndex.name: swBpduProtectionPortIndex

swBpduProtectionPortState.name: swBpduProtectionPortState

swBpduProtectionUnderAttackingTrap.name: swBpduProtectionUnderAttackingTrap

swBpduProtectionRecoveryTrap.name: swBpduProtectionRecoveryTrap

swBpduProtectionRecoveryMethod.description: This object indicates the method of recovery from BPDU under attack.
